<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/41231177-chickenmittens">Chickenmittens</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I'm late to answer this, but that's kind of the point actually. Most of the ground fighting was pointless, with the real work being done by ships and <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I'm late to answer this, but that's kind of the point actually. Most of the ground fighting was pointless, with the real work being done by ships and aircraft. The grunts were just given vague, pointless orders, then marched out to die.<br /><br />"Most of the time, Im bored. When I'm not bored, I'm scared."<br /><br />Remember, the author was a grunt in Vietnam, and the book is based very heavily on this.<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
